section.section:
A receiving track's commission on interstate wagering, after deduction of applicable taxes and any amounts required to be paid by contract to the track from which the interstate simulcast originated, shall be split as follows:
Twenty-five percent (25%) to the purse program of the receiving track;
Twenty-five percent (25%) to the purse program of the host track;
Twenty-five percent (25%) to the receiving track; and
Twenty-five percent (25%) to the host track.
